This product bundles third-party software, vendored under
`public/apps/pptx-viewer/vendor/` (each retains its own license):

- PPTXjs (the .pptx → HTML renderer, incl. divs2slides) — MIT — © Meshesha;
  https://github.com/meshesha/PPTXjs (vendored from commit 1a9260b).
  Upstream license text: `public/apps/pptx-viewer/vendor/LICENSE.PPTXjs`.
- d3.js — ISC/BSD-3-Clause — © Mike Bostock; https://d3js.org
- nvd3 (nv.d3) — Apache-2.0 — © Novus Partners; https://github.com/novus/nvd3
- JSZip — MIT or GPLv3 (dual) — © Stuart Knightley; https://stuk.github.io/jszip
- jquery.fullscreen — MIT — https://github.com/private-face/jquery.fullscreen

These files are bundled (rather than loaded from a CDN) for reproducibility and
to avoid an unpinned upstream; they are not part of this app's MIT-licensed code.
